[ctns_make id='gen_abs_absolute_value']

  [ctns_front style='']
Absolute Value
  [/ctns_front]  

  [ctns_back style='width:80%;font-size:90%;']
$| |x| =   \begin{cases} \ \ \ x, & \text{if } \ x \ge 0 \\ -x, & \text{if } \ x \lt 0 \end{cases} |$
  [/ctns_back]  

  [ctns_backspeak]
The absolute value of x --  equals x -- if x is greater than or  equal to zero, -- other wise the absolute value of x -- equals negative x.
  [/ctns_backspeak]  

[/ctns_make]
